items.title: Quantum Machines launches Qualibrate open source framework to speed quantum computer calibration
items.description: Quantum Machines, a provider of advanced hybrid quantum-classical control solutions, announced today the release of Qualibrate.

items.title: Foxconn builds AI factory in partnership with Taiwan and Nvidia
